title: Which K-pop idols are most liked by non-fans? - Quora

response.answer_text: I think that this really also goes with popular idols that everybody knows even if they don’t stan. These are a few in my opinion. Jae -Day6  Mark -NCT  Eric Nam (Literally all fandoms just collectively stan him, and just most of Dive Studios for the matter)  Here’s the “group” at Dive Studios that most people stan. Jamie, Amber, Ashley, BM, Peniel, Jae, Eric. Oop and AleXa is a new addition. (Don’t forget eddie, diana, and everyone alse who works there too :)  Ryujin -Itzy  Jackson Wang -Got7 (TEAM WANG YALL) (requested by Kristy Lustre)  Johnny -NCT (I feel like people who don't actually stan NCT usually bias either Mark, Johnny, or Taeyong)  And the last one is very unknown, many people don't even this know group, but this is for the gay ladies… Miya -GWSN  Yes anybody who’s discovered her has a crush on her, idc what gender you are. Peace out! -Kyubin (규빈)

I know one that strikes out for me is Taemin. Now the way I'm interpreting this question is like idols who have fans outside of their group. Taemin has several solo albums. Japanese solo albums as well. One can say he's accomplished alot on his own. I don't want to start fan wars about solo stans and what not, but it would be hard to deny that Taemin has a lot of fans who only like him for his solo work. I know that for me when I show off his solo work, I generally get a good response from people who are outsiders to kpop. Several times I've also had people enjoy his music so much to the point that they actively listen to it. This is just my experience though. I feel like with kpop the stigma it holds about the obsessive fans turns people off. But often times if they gave the artist a chance they'll find that they'll see they create music with similar tastes that they like. There's definitely other idols who are liked by non fans, it just depends who you ask. Sorry if I misinterpreted the question, but I hope this is a good answer. Have a great day ❤

-Bts Taehyung, remember when “Boy With Luv” came out? Everyone was like “who’s the boy with blue hair?” Also, I asked a non-fan who’s her bias and she said Taehyung! She said listened to Singularity and his other songs already. -Of course, Jae form Day6. Since he’s released tracks of his own, so many people listened to him! He’s also active on Instagram and Twitter! His talk shows, his humor, and everything about him make people love him! -Eric Nam, of course, let’s not forget about him! First of all, He speaks english and he has an outstanding personality! People love it! His music is also absolutely fantastic too. I get why so many non fans stan him. ~mochi
